flowchart TD
    Start([User Clicks Button]) --> Trigger[Trigger Click Event]
    Trigger --> Validate[Validate Input/Action]
    Validate --> Check{Valid?}
    Check -->|Yes| Execute[Execute Button Function]
    Check -->|No| Error[Show Error Message]
    Error --> End([End])
    Execute --> Update[Update UI/State]
    Update --> Feedback[Provide User Feedback]
    Feedback --> End
